verbose_text: Among the actionable hypotheses, it was predicted that the p.E326K and p.I368T mutations could lead to a gain of a catalytic residue, p.T369M could lead to a loss of a catalytic residue and p.N370S and p.E326K could increase the glycosylation of the protein.
evidence: p.E326K and p.I368T mutations could lead to a gain
